column5: I'm to Florida Tomorrow Morning and I probably won't have internet access while i'm there  I'd like to wish everyone a Merry Christmas  I should be back to make the swill
Merry Christmas to you too!  Have a great trip.
Have a great trip and a great holidays season
Hey Goran you and the family have yerselfs a great vaction.No internet in Florida? I dont believe it for one second.LOL   Happy holidays dude.
Goran, you have a great trip   and a Merry Christmas.  Look forward to seeing you at the swill.
Have a great trip Goran! I hear diamond rings are cheaper down there Hey TonyB, Uncle Buck is coming to the Swill, better tell them to order more wings in
Merry Christmas Goran, hope you have a great trip.
have fun down south! Merry Christmas!  Cheers!
Have a Merry Christmas and relax and enjoy yourself while you're there  Joey
Merry Christmas Goran!! Have a great time bud!!
Have a safe trip and MERRY CHRISTMAS!!!!
Merry Christmas to you Uncle Buck. Have a great Christmas and a safe trip.  Mike
Have a good one yourself UB. And a merry merry to all the OFC'ers.
Trade snow for sand.... sounds good to me Have a safe trip and enjoy the holidays!    Whopper

I'll save 2 seats for you....and one for Andrea too.  Have a blast you big palooka.  Hey, I hear there's a tiny body of water down there with some great fishing. Atlantic Ocean/Carribean Sea...or something like that.  See if ya can bring us back some fishing pictures.
